<paragraph blockId="21.[96,652,817,967]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">The male has prominent spots like a leopard, hence the name. Note the pair of vertical yellow- orange stripes on each flap of the fan. This species is known only from areas near the southern coast of Western Australia.</paragraph>
